            <div class="field field--media--field-caption field--name-field-caption field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><h2>Investigating Greenland's Glaciers</h2><p>Larry Mayer, Brian Calder, and Elizabeth Weidner represented CCOM during the <a href="https://www.polar.se/en/expeditions/previous-expeditions/arctic/geoeo-north-of-greenland-2024/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GEOEO North of Greenland 2024</a> expedition to the remote Victoria Fjord aboard the I/B <em>Oden</em>. Findings from the expedition have been published in <a href="https://www.nature.com/articles/s43247-026-03666-x" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nature's Communications Earth &amp; Environment</a>, offering new insight into the evolution of glaciers in northern Greenland.</p><p><a class="more-link" href="https://www.facebook.com/reel/1456312953192209/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Watch the video</a></p></div>
      
      </div>
    </div>
  
</li>
                  <li>

  

  
