            <div class="field field--media--field-caption field--name-field-caption field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><h2>We're hiring!</h2><p>CCOM has created two new positions to support our efforts in cartography and navigation. Please use the links for more details and for instructions on how to apply.</p><p><a class="more-link" href="https://usnh.wd5.myworkdayjobs.com/Careers/job/University-of-New-Hampshire--Main-Campus/Research-Scientist-II_JR7282" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Research Scientist II</a></p><p><a class="more-link" href="https://usnh.wd5.myworkdayjobs.com/Careers/job/University-of-New-Hampshire--Main-Campus/Postdoctoral-Research-Associate_JR7277" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Postdoctoral Research Associate</a></p></div>
      
