            <div class="field field--media--field-caption field--name-field-caption field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><h2>Mapping in Arctic Waters</h2><p>In this video from Seabed 2030, CCOM researcher Kevin Jerram is one of the expedition members aboard the I/B Oden who gives us a glimpse of what it's like to map the ocean floor in Arctic waters.</p><p><a class="more-link" href="https://www.facebook.com/reel/1244788870464964/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Watch the video</a></p></div>
      
