              <div class="field__item">  <div class="para__padding para__padding--top-big unh-paragraphs-layout-behavior paragraphs-behavior-style--padding--top-big paragraph paragraph--type--layout paragraph--view-mode--default">
          
      <div class="para__layout__grid--gutter-wide para__layout__grid para__layout__grid--3 para__layout" id="para-layout-grid--2">
    
                <div class="para__layout__item paragraph paragraph--type--unh-simple-text paragraph--view-mode--default clearfix">
              

  
            <div class="field field--paragraph--field-paragraph-content field--name-field-paragraph-content field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><div class="text-align-center h4">CCOM in the <a>News</a></div><hr class="hr--quarter-width"><p><a href="https://ecomagazine.com/news/research/historic-expedition-reveals-hidden-seafloor-influence-on-greenland-glacier/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Historic Expedition Reveals Hidden Seafloor Influence on Greenland Glacier</strong></a><br><em>Environment<span> Coastal &amp; Offshore</span></em><span>, June 11, 2026</span></p><hr><p><a href="https://nautiluslive.org/blog/2026/06/08/ev-nautilus-installs-new-em304-multibeam-sonar-explore-deeper-and-more-ever" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>E/V Nautilus Installs New EM304 Multibeam Sonar to Explore Deeper and More Than Ever!</strong></a><br><em>Nautilus Live Blog</em>, June 8, 2026</p><hr><p><a href="https://nautiluslive.org/blog/2026/06/09/launching-na178-expedition-starting-2026-mapping-deeper-ever" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Launching the NA178 Expedition: Starting 2026 Mapping Deeper Than Ever!</strong></a><br><em>Nautilus Live Blog</em>, June 6, 2026</p><hr><p><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/23/climate/china-seabed-mining-maps-rare-earths.html?unlocked_article_code=1.dFA.39al.HqwyZbEMMITf&amp;smid=url-share" target="_blank" data-entity-type="external" rel="noopener"><strong>China Publishes Maps Detailing Minerals on the Ocean Floor</strong></a><br><em>New York Times</em>, April 23, 2026</p><hr><p><a href="https://magazine.unh.edu/issue/winter-2026/deep-sea-history/" target="_blank" data-entity-type="external" rel="noopener"><strong>Deep-Sea History</strong></a><br><em>UNH Magazine</em>, March 3, 2026&nbsp;</p><hr><p><a class="more-link" href="/about/ccom-news" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-uuid="335fd838-cc67-4bde-9113-256fb64b1cf6" data-entity-substitution="canonical" title="CCOM in the News">More News</a></p></div>
      
          </div>
  
                <div class="para__layout__item paragraph paragraph--type--unh-simple-text paragraph--view-mode--default clearfix">
              

  
            <div class="field field--paragraph--field-paragraph-content field--name-field-paragraph-content field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><div class="text-align-center h4">Recent Publications</div><hr class="hr--quarter-width"><p><a href="https://www.nature.com/articles/s43247-026-03666-x" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Atlantic Water Access and the Break-up of the C.H. Ostenfeld Gletsjer Ice Tongue, Northwest Greenland</strong></a><br>Jakobsson. M, Kirchner, N., Nilsson, J., Stranne, C., Mayer, L., Barnett, J., Felicity A., Holmes, F.A., Calder, B., et al., <em>Communications Earth &amp; Environment</em>, 7(493), 2026 .</p><hr><p><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.ecoinf.2026.103829" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span><strong>A Multi-Source, Remote Sensing-Driven Framework for Detecting Structural and Compositional Change in Coral Reefs</strong></span></a><br>Trudeau, G.A., Lowell, K., Dijkstra, J.A., <em>Ecological Informatics,</em> 96. 2026.</p><hr><p><a href="https://www.hydro-international.com/content/article/how-multibeam-echosounder-platform-choice-controls-mapping-resolution" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>How Multibeam Echosounder Platform Choice Controls Mapping Resolution</strong></a><br><span>Adediran, E., </span><em><span>Hydro International #4 - 2025 BUSINESS GUIDE</span></em><span>, 2026.</span></p><hr><p><a class="more-link" href="/publications" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-uuid="8d4824c4-2f45-4107-84e2-d84097f8214c" data-entity-substitution="canonical" title="Publications">More Publications</a></p></div>
      
          </div>
  
                <div class="para__layout__item paragraph paragraph--type--unh-simple-text paragraph--view-mode--default clearfix">
              

  
            <div class="field field--paragraph--field-paragraph-content field--name-field-paragraph-content field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><div class="text-align-center h4">Events</div><hr class="hr--quarter-width"><p><a href="/event/2026/06/unified-operational-framework-interpolation-uncertainty-bathymetry-estimation-integration" target="_blank" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-uuid="c0ba84be-1ddd-4c78-9859-0d11d240ac27" data-entity-substitution="canonical" rel="noopener" title="A Unified Operational Framework for Interpolation Uncertainty in Bathymetry: Estimation, Integration, and Application to Adaptive Hydrographic Survey Design"><span><strong>A Unified Operational Framework for Interpolation Uncertainty in Bathymetry: Estimation, Integration, and Application to Adaptive Hydrographic Survey Design</strong></span></a><br>Elias Adediran, Ph.D. Thesis Proposal Defense<br>Ocean Engineering<br>Wednesday, June 10, 2026, 11:00am<br>Chase 105</p><hr><p><a href="/event/2026/05/subsampled-graph-based-bathymetric-data-processing" target="_blank" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-uuid="d22d46c8-e135-440f-b441-a6cce4f43a5f" data-entity-substitution="canonical" rel="noopener" title="Subsampled Graph-Based Bathymetric Data Processing"><span><strong>Subsampled Graph-Based Bathymetric Data Processing</strong></span></a><br>Adriano Fonseca, Ph.D. Thesis Proposal Defense<br>Ocean Engineering<br>Thursday, May 21, 2026, 9:00am<br>Chase 130</p><hr><p><a href="/event/2026/05/its-not-just-depth-estimating-uncertainty-interpolated-bathymetry" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-uuid="6c5bfb78-87ef-419a-ada5-db84b257f33e" data-entity-substitution="canonical" title="It’s Not Just Depth: Estimating Uncertainty in Interpolated Bathymetry"><span><strong>It’s Not Just Depth: Estimating Uncertainty in Interpolated Bathymetry</strong></span></a><br><span>Elias Adediran, Doctoral Researcher</span><br><span>UNH CCOM/JHC</span><br>Friday, May 1, 2026, 3:10pm<br>Chase 105&nbsp;</p><hr><p><a class="more-link" href="/outreach/seminars" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-uuid="59d9097e-bd83-41ec-bebb-1133842a36fc" data-entity-substitution="canonical" title="Seminars">More Events</a></p></div>
      
          </div>
  
    
